Here are the minimal amount of x dependencies needed:
x11-libs/libX11
x11-base/xorg-server
x11-apps/xinit
x11-libs/libXrandr
x11-libs/libxft
x11-apps/xrandr

Other optional stuff:
Feh - Wallpapers
Compton - Transparency
x11-libs/libXinerama - Multiple monitors
x11-misc/unclutter - Hide mouse after 3 seconds of idle
libxft - fancy unicode
x11-misc/xclip - Terminal clipboard
I don't use xsetroot because I have dwmstatus already.

# Sound 
media-sound/alsa-utils
idk, I need to do some research to find a minimal but easy to use setup

# File manager
lf - cli based file manager

# Font 
jetbrains-mono - yep

